        <underline method="pen" type="straight" language="LA" text="Vereor ne aut molestus sim vobis Iudices, aut ne ingeniis vestris videar diffidere, si de tam perspicuis rebus diutius disseram"/>
        <underline method="pen" type="straight" language="LA" text="de quibus quoniam verbo arguit, verbo satis est"/>
        <underline method="pen" type="straight" language="LA" text="qud certu[m] est non facere"/>
        <underline method="pen" type="straight" language="LA" text="tametsi neque omnia dica[m] &amp; leuiter vnu[m]quodque tangam. neque enim id facerem, nisi necesse esset. &amp; id erit signi me inuitum facere: 
